  "body": "**Steps to reproduce:**\r\n1. Go to the 1-1 chat\r\n2. Send the message: \"Test_A\"\r\n3. Leave a reply: \"Test_B\"\r\n4. Pin the message\r\n5. Remove replied message \"Test_A\"\r\n6. Open the list of pinned messages\r\n7. Remove the pinned message using 'delete for everyone' option\r\n8. Check the replied message\r\n\r\n**Actual result:**\r\nThe replied message \"Test_A\" is shown after removing\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52490791/214904661-2b3cea83-a4c0-404d-a67d-8acd01d516b9.mp4\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52490791/214905430-945781e5-553c-4bed-93e0-e9c6c55f6c80.png)\r\n\r\n**Expected result:**\r\nThe pinned message is shown as removed in the chat\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52490791/206505607-79f9bf49-0797-4747-ba3a-f7d44ce11a87.png)\r\n\r\n",
